{"original_text": "#早课习字# 董其昌是明代著名书法家, 他看不起前辈书法家赵孟頫, 但是话说的极有分寸, 止于技艺探讨。不像今天的某些人, 尚未入道, 却舍我其谁。", "evtlist": [629], "uid": "1263406744", "dep": 0, "text": "#早课习字# 董其昌是明代著名书法家, 他看不起前辈书法家赵孟頫, 但是话说的极有分寸, 止于技艺探讨。不像今天的某些人, 尚未入道, 却舍我其谁。", "pid": "", "tr": 36, "mid": "3881832997002202", "times": 1, "childnum": 25, "t": 1440984570, "totalChildren": 36, "dr": 25, "children": [{"evtlist": [629], "uid": "2742492057", "dep": 0, "text": "把头像换成你的字吧，扬长避短", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881833588230086", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1440984710, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "爱鸟乐"}, {"evtlist": [629], "uid": "1777881733", "dep": 0, "text": "某些人, 尚未入道, 却舍我其谁……请对号入座吧！", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881833819318292", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1440984766, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "寿安一白丁"}, {"evtlist": [629], "uid": "2368205073", "dep": 0, "text": "貌似董其昌是因为看不起赵孟頫的人品而看不起他的书法", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881833986985650", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1440984805, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "0o00_oo00"}, {"evtlist": [629], "uid": "2076333235", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881833983302827", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1440984805, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "XUEYUTAIHANG"}, {"evtlist": [629], "uid": "2024089951", "dep": 0, "text": "自比赵孟頫？自恋or自黑？", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881834796472684", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1440984998, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "欲犀蚊子"}, {"evtlist": [629], "uid": "1685156335", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881836142559530", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1440985319, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "春江樵夫"}, {"evtlist": [629], "uid": "2556248182", "dep": 0, "text": "转发微博", "pid": "3881832997002202", "tr": 0, "mid": "3881837221297735", "times": 1, "childn